<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger.IsLogSeverityEnabled" Title="IsLogSeverityEnabled method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger">ILogger</PageRef> ->
    IsLogSeverityEnabled
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>IsLogSeverityEnabled</TypeRef> method reports whether the logger currently accepts messages at the supplied severity.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Important">
      <Paragraph>
        Use this method to avoid constructing expensive log messages when the target severity is disabled.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[bool IsLogSeverityEnabled(Severity severity) const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="Severity!cobalt.logging.ILogger.Severity" Name="severity">The severity value to test.</ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="bool">
        <TypeRef>true</TypeRef> if the supplied severity is enabled; otherwise <TypeRef>false</TypeRef>.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger.Severity">ILogger.Severity</PageRefListEntry>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.logging.LogManager.IsLogSeverityEnabled">LogManager.IsLogSeverityEnabled</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
